<div class="row">
  <p>
    Tired of not being able to see the most popular memes of the day or all time. Bookmark this site and check in from time to time.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you don't see your college here, shoot me a mail at <a href="mailto:nam@nambrot.com">nam@nambrot.com</a>, or on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/namchuhoai">Facebook</a> via FBMessage.
  </p>
  <p>If you have the data, you can also add it here:</p>
  <%= form_for @college, :url => colleges_path, :html => {:class => "nice"} do |f| %>
      <label>Name:</label>
     <%= f.text_field :name, :class => 'nice input-text' %>
           <label>Short Name:</label>
     <%= f.text_field :short, :class => 'nice input-text' %>
          <label>Url:</label>
    <%= f.text_field :url, :class => 'nice input-text' %>
    <%= f.submit "Create" %>
  <% end %>
  <p>
    If you like this, maybe you wanna check out <a href="http://fbphotobrowser.herokuapp.com">my facebook photo viewer</a>. You can also view the source of this website is on <a href="https://github.com/nambrot/Campusmemes">Github</a>. My personal website is at <a href="http://www.nambrot.com">www.nambrot.com</a>.
  </p>
</div>